@BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5050

### Login
POST {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@bmpcommerce.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Usuário atual (cole o token retornado pelo login acima)
GET {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar produtos
GET {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/produtos?search=
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar clientes
GET {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar cliente
POST {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/clientes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Cliente Exemplo",
  "cpfCnpj": "390.533.447-05",
  "telefone": "(11) 91234-5678",
  "email": "cliente@exemplo.com",
  "cidade": "São Paulo",
  "estado": "SP",
  "observacoes": null
}

### Listar vendas
GET {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/vendas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Registrar venda (troque os GUIDs por ids reais; clienteId pode ser null = balcão)
POST {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/vendas
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clienteId": null,
  "itens": [
    { "produtoId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000", "quantidade": 2 }
  ]
}

### Cancelar venda (soft delete + estorno de estoque)
POST {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/vendas/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancelar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard (indicadores + vendas por dia)
GET {{BMPCommerce.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
